</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="7.[188,1398,313,410]" pageId="7" pageNumber="8">Male (n = 3): Total length 8.0–10.0, carapace 4.1–4.4 long, femur I 5.6–6.8 long. Palpal tibia 2.8–3.0 long, 0.5–0.6 wide. Female (n = 8): total length 10.0–12.4, carapace 4.8–5.4 long, femur I 5.2–5.6 long. Palpal tarsus 1.4–1.6 long.</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
